caption.text:
The 15th CENS UI is the biggest and most innovative civil engineering event held by Universitas Indonesia. It consists of several series of events with this year's grand theme, "Resilient City: Developing Urban Transportation". Resilient city is an urban concept that can sustain existing community activities in spite of natural disasters and demographic structure changes. The concept of urban development uses several aspects, one of which is the development of infrastructure and transportation system that can support the mobility of a community.

I, Irvan Affandi, suggest you to join The 15th CENS UI series of events:1. Create an innovation for a better Indonesia, and win over USD 1650!

Register: http://cfi.cens-ui.com2. Compete with civil engineering students all over Indonesia and win the first National Tender Competition!

Register: http://ntc.cens-ui.com3. Discuss the latest issues in Civil Engineering especially in sustainable and resilient infrastructure with various reputable speakers by joining the Conference on Resilient City Issues.Join us: http://cens-ui.comThe 15th CENS UI #dontmissyourcens
